snippet.title: Custody Full Movie | 2023 New Released Hindi Dubbed Movie | Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani
snippet.description:
Here's presenting "CUSTODY" the Hindi Dubbed Version of the Telugu action thriller Film "CUSTODY", starring Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Anandhi, R. Sarath Kumar, Jiiva and Sampath Raj in lead roles.    

Movie (Hindi Dubbed):- Custody 
Original Movie Name:- Custody in Telugu 
StarCast:- Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Jiiva, R. Sarath Kumar, Sampath Raj, Anandhi
Music:- Yuvan Shankar Raja, Ilaiyaraaja 
Producer:- Srinivasaa Chituri 
Director:- Venkat Prabhu 

Constable Shiva is assigned to escort a witness from police custody to the courtroom. However, he soon learns Shiva that the entire police department wants the witness dead.

Episode 3932: Sundar Ka Waada
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal is concerned that Sundar is not fulfilling his word as he is not picking up his calls or answering text messages. To get Daya back, he arranges for Taarak and himself to travel to Ahmedabad. He visits Taarak's place who were planning to go shopping together. Jetha meets Bhide and Sodhi in the compound and asks the reason for his sadness to which he tells them about the uncooked plan of Daya's arrival. Watch the episode.

snippet.title: FilterCopy | Falling In Love After Arranged Marriage | Ft. Anshuman Malhotra,  Esha Kansara
snippet.description:
From arranged marriage to happily ever after, we found love ‚ù§Ô∏è

Approximately 12 million in India are living with epilepsy* - a neurological condition. It is surrounded by social stigma and taboos that emanate due to lack of correct information. 

Sanofi (India) wants to change that!

This film helps bust many common myths about epilepsy, so the right information can help spread awareness. Watch it to rid yourself of any misconceptions about epilepsy!  Like and share it with your network, so you help educate others, too. 

This can be your pledge to spread the word about what's right. 
To know more on epilepsy and how it can be managed, visit: http://surl.sanofi.com/daretoknowepilepsy

*Reference - Epilepsy in India I: Epidemiology and public health - PMC (nih.gov), available at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4564458/

Welcome to our channel, where we delve into the intriguing world of cricket controversies! In this video, we explore the recent claims made by Pakistani players, shedding light on their allegations against India's victories in World Cup matches. From ball tampering to DRS manipulation and even accusations of cheating in the toss, the cricketing rivalry between India and Pakistan takes a new turn.

Hasan Raza, a former Pakistani cricketer, ignited the fire by suggesting that the Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI) is providing different balls to Indian bowlers, giving them an unfair advantage in swinging conditions. The plot thickens as we dissect this claim and examine the evidence, separating fact from fiction.

But the drama doesn't end there. Some Pakistani players have raised eyebrows about the Decision Review System (DRS), alleging that India has found a way to manipulate the system in their favor. Join us as we analyze these allegations, exploring the intricacies of the DRS and whether there's any truth to the accusations.

Sikander Bakht's recent statement about India allegedly cheating in the toss adds another layer to the controversy. We break down the claims, providing context and examining the impact of the toss on match outcomes. Is there a strategic advantage at play, or are these allegations merely a product of rivalry and competition?

To offer a balanced perspective, we delve into the history of cross-border cricketing banter. Inzamam ul Haq's revelation about the Pakistani team attempting to convert Harbhajan Singh to Islam adds an interesting twist. Additionally, we feature Javed Miandad's controversial statements about Ram Mandir, providing insights into the complex relationship between cricket and socio-political narratives.

As we present this comprehensive exploration, it's essential to consider whether these claims are rooted in genuine concerns or if they're fueled by the age-old rivalry between India and Pakistan. We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Naam tere saari ki saari bahaarein kardun

Tere rang se mil raha hai

Dil mera tere sang
Baith kar kyon khil raha hai

O mere janaab
Hai koi jawaab
Is baat ka

Is sharam ke lehje ko pehchaniye to
Baat ban jayegi baat maniye to

Kya hai kuch nahi ye char din ki zindagani
Taaron ke her fer ki ye karistani
Na kabhi bhi mitne wali likh dein kahani

Aapki aankhon mein jo likha hai wo main padh raha hun

Baat wo honth par kab aayegi
Intezaar kar raha hun

Hai koi jawaab
O mere janaab
Hai koi jawaab

Bunte rahein 
Ya na bune ye khaab
Hai koi jawaab
Is baat ka

snippet.title: Highlights || Bhilwara Kings VS India Capitals || 1st Match || Legends League Cricket 2023
snippet.description:
Highlights || Bhilwara Kings VS India Capitals || 1st Match || Legends League Cricket 2023

#legendsleaguecricket2023  #LLCT20 #BossLogonKaGame



About : Legends League Cricket

Legends League Cricket is dedicated to cricket lovers and is a pioneer in offering a platform where retired cricket players can demonstrate their skills, engage with fans, and sense the thrill of cricket once again. The league is dedicated to bring cricket enthusiasts from all walks of life together to celebrate this exciting sport. 

At Legends League Cricket, there are two distinctive cricketing formats being played: Regional and Franchise. Each format gives the game its own charm and competitiveness, providing players and fans with a combination of exciting encounters. 

Legends League Cricket introduced its global format, LLC Masters in 2022 in an effort to push the limits of cricketing excellence. Its inaugural season was hosted by Muscat, Oman, and the most recent season was hosted by Doha, Qatar. The three teams that compete in this format to showcase the best of talent: Indian Maharajas, Asia Lions, and World Giants. Representing the nation‚Äôs cricket-crazy culture, India Maharajas bring together the best Indian talent. Asia Lions represent the cricketing powerhouses of Asia. And, a fiery blend of international talent makes up the team of World Giants. 

It has also presented the franchise-based edition of Legends League Cricket, which is held in India. Four privately owned teams compete in this exciting tournament: India Capitals, Gujarat Giants, Bhilwara Kings, and Manipal Tiger. India Capitals team is owned by GMR Sportsline, which also co-owns the IPL team Delhi Capitals. Gujarat Giants team is owned by Adani Sportline, which also owns Gujarat Giants team in the Women's Premier League (WPL). Bhilwara Kings is owned by The LNJ Bhilwara Group. Manipal Tigers is owned by Manipal Education and Medical Group. Two new teams joined the second season, Urbanrisers Hyderabad which is owned by the prestigious Urbanrise Group in collaboration with Mr. JC Pavan Reddy, and Southern Super Stars which is owned by KLO Sports with Ranjeeth Rathod.

Absolute Legends Sports Pvt. Ltd. is the owner and operator of Legends League Cricket. It aspires to create a cricket community where legendary players from around the world come once again to compete and inspire. 

The Upcoming season of Legends League Cricket will be held in India from November to December. Legends League Cricket reinvents passion for cricket, sportsmanship, and competition. Let‚Äôs celebrate the spirit of cricket together.

know more : https://www.llct20.com/
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/llct20
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/llct20/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/llct20

snippet.title: Yo Yo Honey Singh on Love, Heartbreak, Betrayal | Honey Singh Podcast | Sadhika Sehgal | MLR Ep 32
snippet.description:
Today we are in conversation with the much-awaited guest, none other than the G.O.A.T., Yo Yo Honey Singh! 

Known for laying the foundations of the OG gang, Mafia Mundeer, that gave a different hype to the Indian rap industry, Honey Singh has successfully dominated the music scene with his catchy tunes and energetic performances, on and off-screen.

As we unpack the numerous layers to his personal and professional journey in this episode with Sadhika Sehgal, we are spilling the tea on everything‚Äîfrom his wildest dreams to the secret sauce that keeps him at the top of the game. And yes, we're even dishing on that epic meet-up with the legend himself, AR Rahman.

From his latest songs to his upcoming documentary on Netflix, catch the ‚ÄòAngreji Beat‚Äô fame share his thoughts on rising to fame and the fallback he experienced. 

Ever wondered what life means to Yo Yo Honey Singh? Or why do his fans adore him so much? We're getting real on all that and more‚Äîhow he handles the haters, the times he's been misunderstood, and his advice for non-believers in God and the astrological realm.

We're taking you behind the scenes of his life, exploring the lessons he learned from the tough times, his fearless attitude, and, of course, the lowdown on love and heartbreak. Ishq versus pyaar, his school gang stories, thoughts on karma‚Äîyou name it, we're chatting about it.

Curious about his take on male friendships and what "mardangi" (masculinity) means to him? We've got the deets. Plus, we're delving into his unconventional career advice for those who can't stand the 9-to-5 grind, and the real talk on toxic traits.

Buckle up for the ride as we spill the tea on his concert moments, including that one time he got a little heated, and yes, even his mom giving him an earful.

Don't forget to watch an exclusive peek into the life and mind of Yo Yo Honey Singh, showcasing his emotional side for the very first time on the big screen!  To know more about our Desi Kalaakar watch the full episode and get ready for all the feels!

‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•ç‡§°‡§µ ‡§®‡•É‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø | Episode 02 - Melodies of India 

While walking from Gangotri, following the river Ganga I came across this beautiful little village called Bagori in Harshil, Uttarakhand. 
To my pure luck I was at the right time at the right place as I got to witness the most famous festival of Uttarakhand, that is ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•ç‡§°‡§µ ‡§®‡•É‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø  

Pandav dance is a folk dance of Uttarakhand. This dance is related to the lives of the five Pandavas of the Mahabharata period. Pandavas and Draupadi are worshiped through this dance

This festival takes place every year on the sixth day of Navratri

==========================================================

Heading onto a new journey, that's shape me inside out :) 

What is Melodies of India? 

Magic Monkey, a new age travel YouTube channel travelled and explored by Raunaq Sahni is thrilled to announce an extraordinary and ambitious project. In the quest to unravel the soul of India, Raunaq embarks on a six-month odyssey across the country, meticulously documenting the essence of what it truly means to be Indian. 

The "Melodies of India" project as envisioned by Raunaq is an expedition that aims to capture the heart and spirit of India, transcending its deep-rooted cultures into a visually captivating series of photographs and videos, each narrating a unique facet of our incredible nation. These photographs and videos will serve as visual testimonies, encapsulating the diversity, traditions, and modernisation of India. 

He will later publish 11 photographs along with the moving stories in a Photobook.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3931 | 17 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3931: Jethalal Gets Impatient
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha urgently phones all of Sundar's phone numbers, but he is never able to contact him. Jetha is relieved when an uncle who is Daya's neighbor answers the phone. Jetha asks the elderly guy to connect him with Daya. The old guy pays a visit to Daya's home, but he informs Jetha that she is not there. Sundar even ignores Tapu's call. Why did Sundar not answer his phone?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3931, 17 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

‚úçüèªùêëùêÑùêÇùêàùêèùêÑ:
ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêÄùê¶ùê•ùêö ùêÇùê°ùêÆùê≠ùêßùêûùê≤, wash the Gooseberry/Amla & grate it. Keep the pan on the flame, and put some Ghee, Fennel Seeds, Cumin Seeds, Green Cardamom, grated Gooseberry/Amla, Jaggery, and Sugar. Mix well & cook on a high flame. Add Balck Salt, Rock Salt, Coriander Powder, Red Chili Powder, Kashmiri Red Chili Powder, Chat Masala and roasted Cumin Powder. Mix well & cook it till it gets dry. Then Add some Dried Ginger Powder and Melon Seeds. Then keep it for cooling down. 
ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêåùêÆùê´ùêöùêõùêõùêö, soak Gooseberries overnight. Wipe them and prick them with the fork. Boil Water and add Amla. Cover and cook for 5-7 minutes. In a pan add Candy Sugar/Mishri, pricked & boiled Gooseberries/Amla, and Water. Stir it continuously, cover it, and cook on a slow flame for 40-45 minutes. When the Amla color changed & Syrup turned thicker then put the flame off and take it out. Add Cardamom Powder, Black Salt, and Dry Ginger Powder and mix it well. 
ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêÄùê¶ùê•ùêö ùêåùê¢ùê´ùêúùê° ùêÄùêúùê°ùêöùê´, in a pan, put Water and Amla. keep it boiling for 3-4 mins then add some, Salt and cover it. After 3-4 mins Check the Gooseberries. Then add long chopped Green Chili and cover it. after cooling down. take it out in a glass jar then add Lemon Juice and enjoy.
ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêÄùê¶ùê•ùêö ùêÜùêöùê≠ùêöùê†ùêöùê≠, In a cooker, add water, and Amla and give 2 whistles. Then grind it. In the same cooker, add ground Amla, Jaggery Roasted Cumin Powder, Dried Ginger Powder, Asafoetida, Carom Seeds, Black Pepper, Black Salt, Rock Salt, and Amchoor Powder. Cook until it gets dry. Then keep it cool and make a small ball. Wrap it with Powdered Sugar. Keep it in a fresh jar and enjoy!

snippet.title: Door Aa Gaye (Official Video) Vishal Mishra, Dino James | VYRL Originals
snippet.description:
"Door Aa Gaye" brings together two of the most exciting musical talent together for the first time. The gifted Vishal Mishra - fresh from the success of Zihaal e Miskin & popular hip hop star Dino James - fresh out of his win from Khatron Ke Khiladi - combine forces for an unique collaboration - producing Door Aa Gaye. A lilting love track that merges the melodic vocals of Vishal and the hip-hop vibe of Dino, this one is a definite for those moody nights, when the party moves from dancing tracks to soulful soothing melodies. Door Aa Gaye is new age ode to love and longing.

localized.description:
"Door Aa Gaye" brings together two of the most exciting musical talent together for the first time. The gifted Vishal Mishra - fresh from the success of Zihaal e Miskin & popular hip hop star Dino James - fresh out of his win from Khatron Ke Khiladi - combine forces for an unique collaboration - producing Door Aa Gaye. A lilting love track that merges the melodic vocals of Vishal and the hip-hop vibe of Dino, this one is a definite for those moody nights, when the party moves from dancing tracks to soulful soothing melodies. Door Aa Gaye is new age ode to love and longing.

#DoorAaGaye #VishalMishra #DinoJames

snippet.title: Sam‡§¨‡§π‡§æ‡§¶‡•Å‡§∞ - Sam Ka Bahadur BTS | Vicky Kaushal | Meghna Gulzar | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 01.12.2023
snippet.description:
Feel the pulse of patriotism as Vicky Kaushal transforms into Sam Manekshaw, narrating a captivating story of dedication, honour, and unwavering courage in this exclusive BTS video.

#Sam‡§¨‡§π‡§æ‡§¶‡•Å‡§∞ in cinemas 1.12.2023

#SamIsHere #sambahadur 

Sam‡§¨‡§π‡§æ‡§¶‡•Å‡§∞ is a tribute to Field Marshal Sam HFJ Manekshaw, MC, India's first Field Marshal and a legendary Army General. His career witnessed the shaping of India's geopolitical borders, and his life was marked by significant milestones, from fighting in World War II to being the Chief of Army Staff during the 1971 Indo-Pakistan war, that led to the creation of Bangladesh.
This RSVP film explores his dynamic personality and his unparalleled military career, offering a glimpse into the life of a no-nonsense Army Commander, also known as "Sam Bahadur" by the soldiers he led.

snippet.title: Indians And Diwali | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
A Very Happy Diwali !!!

Special Thanks to Tanishq

As the Title is Indians And Diwali this Video has everything that happens during Diwali Festival . The most relatable and Funny Diwali Video . Scenarios like what happens on Indian families doing Diwali shopping for dhanteras shopping new utensils or jewellery shopping of gold coin , silver coin from brand like Tanishq . Kaamwali and her struggles with house cleaning waiting for diwali gifts , diwali bonus . Daughter painting diya and mom hanging diwali lights . Girls dressing up in traditional dieting whole month to look good and clicking pictures and making videos . Prepations for office diwali pooja , sisters cleaning house and competing and having fun , next day of diwali and taking off the lights , flower garlands , rangoli , giving diwali to staff , guards , kaamwali bai , Aunties for shopping for diwali pooja kheel patashe , patisha , paan , supari , sweets , favourite mathai moti choor ladoo , kaju ki barfi , bondi ke laddoo , cham cham , diwali decoration , bhandan var , diya , lights , candles , rangoli , diwali gifts dry fruits , gift box . Indian Aunties bargaining with shopkeeper , shops making huge profits during diwali dhamaka sales , going out to relatives to wish happy diwali and dealing with diwali 2023 traffic jams , giving gifts to relatives and travelling in car , indian sweets shops fully loaded with customers , eating in restaurants after diwali shopping eating dosa , chowmein , tuition mam helps kids prepare their diwali poem , diwali essay , teaching why diwali is celebrated , diwali school function costumes , diwali is the festival food , every foodie loves puri , aloo , kheer , halwa , muli ki bhujji , raita , achar , panchamrit , laxmi ganesh pooja , talking about the ban on fire crackers , diwali away from home , pg wali diwali , showing of chandi , golf gifts , buying air purifier cause of the air pollution and noise pullution caused by crackers in delhi , south delhi posh diwali partiers playing poker , drinking , tambola , diwali vlogs , diwali outfits , lehenga , suits , saree , kurti , kurta , and looking beautiful and clicking pictures . West Delhi people mocking south delhi on dieting on diwali doing keto , intermittent fasting or just drinking alchol , many more fun things covered in the diwali video .
This video is filled with Festive season memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories of Diwali festival
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour . A very happy diwali 2023 season to all of you and Happy deepawali  .. Comment down your Fav Part , 
Like , Share and

Episode 3930: Sundar Ko Phone Lagao
--------------------------------------------------------
A customer visits the Gada Electronic Store to purchase a gift for his wife, who has been separated, and his brother-in-law keeps pushing back the date of her homecoming. Jetha connects with the customer and tells him about his brother-in-law. Jetha is eager to learn the day on which Daya will return. So he dials Sundar's number, but Sundar has thirteen phone numbers. Jetha is puzzled about which number to dial. Nattu, Kaka, and Bagha attempt to assist him. Will Jetha be able to communicate with Sundar?

Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant.
